title: WRIF Drew and Mike 051513 complete
description:
Drew and Mike, WRIF 101.1 FM Detroit morning show 05 15 13, from 5:57AM (before intro) EST til end of show. Created using audacity 1.3 beta. MP3 format. COMplete, including commercial breaks and WRIF.com's shitty music over the commercials.

Recording, saving, and sharing the last 7 days of 101.1 WRIF's legendary Drew and Mike morning show, cancelled after 22 years.
